Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:47.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Yin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:57.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:17.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:21.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Youko-chan! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It too hot when it's that close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:33.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but this is my first time doing moxibustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,First time, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:41.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe along with this boring remuneration we can pass the time by...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:46.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:49.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come in without even knocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:50.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did the chief say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:58.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He told us to continue with the mission and obtain Izanagi by any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't accomplish the mission, we will be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:08.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh geez, just when I've found a misbehaving cutie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:13.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, would having a tragic past score me more cuteness points?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kill my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You know something, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why were they looking for Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:38.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to kill my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you hate me that much, go ahead and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:50.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd rather die than be a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:51.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What a pacifist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are no replacements for anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:56.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Since everyone is unique!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:57.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:05.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're the kind of person who can kill friends and lovers without batting an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:11.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:13.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was normal up until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly everything is all messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:26.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nor do I want to see other people killing or getting killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've... I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:37.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So they called me in this early in the morning just to clean up the mess the colonel made?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly do they expect me to do with so few people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you requested for more personnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:49.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The brass just doesn't understand how important this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, there is only one novice available
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like there's no choice but to mobilize a large conventional force...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:59.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make us much different from the colonel then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:00.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Should we capture him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know Shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Japanese game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:16.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike chess, you can use the captured pieces as your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:24.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So she cried herself to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:30.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's to be expected. Up until two days ago, she was just a normal middle school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:38.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true that your memories reside outside of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:41.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's only a periodic backup
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:46.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,so I've only heard the conclusion of what happened in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So who are your owners now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:52.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Same as yours, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The CIA?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:55.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:03.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've just come to issue you a change of orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:35.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My mind can't keep up with the changes in my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:40.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure something bad will happen again if we're together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:45.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be okay, Tanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:13.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:20.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:22.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Near Hell's Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:26.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That place is off-limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:28.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is Shion there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:42.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:50.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Episode 3    Vanishing into the Snow Fields...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:55.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, it got disconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But it rang, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:02.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Suou is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to trace it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Tanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:29.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They tracked us through your cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A surveillance spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:42.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:43.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:57.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's the train over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:59.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Try to get on without getting noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll depart in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I made a deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:31.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be rewarded and guaranteed a position if I capture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What about Nika?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:33.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:34.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Shion Pavlichenko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:47.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:52.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like we're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:14.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll just have to go wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mao, take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:26.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, don't blame me if something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Petya! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There is no time for you to be surprised. I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:39.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're going under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come here. You can climb up right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:06.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He'll act as a decoy and distract them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll escape during the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Time for departure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Beware of accidents!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:03.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad. I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:20.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:23.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:28.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:41.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:43.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:49.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:53.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't even know that you had a little brother named Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Does he really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:01.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I let you live...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nika!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:09.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:10.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:14.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back home, Tanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:23.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:42.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She has awoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All contractors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,should just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,120° to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,3 meters up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,10 centimeters more to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,20° to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:18.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,3 meters down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:28.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,110° to the right, 50 centimeters down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:10.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hei! He's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:27.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"With three advantages, there will also be three disadvantages" sums up our situation, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:30.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Mr. Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:37.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you knew where the Black Grim Reaper is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:45.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to tell me that the all-knowing CIA doesn't know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you're here to discuss business, then I'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:52.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Information is my commodity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:59.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My motto is "As long as I receive the proper payment, I will provide information to anyone at anytime."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:03.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"Thus, though we have heard of stupid haste in war."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:08.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I expect a prompt reply, Madame O'Reille.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,His star really disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:15.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If his star fell, that would means he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of one disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't make a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm a bit busy over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:26.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just give up on him. Find yourself a new guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:28.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Kanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:31.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is a good opportunity for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:43.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Kirihara speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:43.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, er... I mean Kirihara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:46.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Saitou, do you have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:50.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:53.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I've got all the time in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:54.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:58.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's regarding BK201...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:05.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm sorry but I can't give out information about contractors to anyone outside the department.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:06.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:11.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If they find out that you were still in touch with someone who was exiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:12.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:16.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Kirihara, you're still the boss to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'll call you another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:26.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of Section 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:29.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Section 3? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:35.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If they ever show up, don't listen to anything they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:37.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:38.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:40.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:42.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ministry of Internal Affairs and Communications?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:49.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:58.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Two years ago, internal information from Public Safety was leaked anonymously to the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:02.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and exposed the existence of contractors to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:07.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But there were no traces found of the so-called Syndicate from which the information was leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:12.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of Section 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:17.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ministry of Internal Affairs and Communications is just a cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:21.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Our objective is to exterminate the remnants of the Syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:26.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and for that purpose we've been authorized to use any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:30.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And what is it that you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:35.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK201 isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:37.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's still lurking in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:42.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able reach him from where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:43.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:51.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:06.70,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:06.70,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:17.21,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:17.21,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:26.77,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:26.77,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:32.95,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:32.95,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.70,0:22:38.05,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.70,0:22:38.05,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:37.68,0:22:42.81,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:22:37.68,0:22:42.81,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:22:42.58,0:22:51.46,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:22:42.58,0:22:51.46,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:51.28,0:22:56.55,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:22:51.28,0:22:56.55,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.29,0:23:03.50,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.29,0:23:03.50,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 6,0:23:03.13,0:23:11.09,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:23:03.13,0:23:11.09,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 7,0:23:11.01,0:23:21.38,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:23:11.01,0:23:21.38,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:31.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you drinking a bit too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:33.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:38.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei, what happened to Yin?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:40.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:43.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:51.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Contractors must remunerate after using their abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.10,0:23:57.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have become a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.15,0:24:05.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)}Without a destination, they drift into a city to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:07.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)}The reflectionless surface of the blue lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.92,0:24:13.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)}The echoes of the gunshot are a requiem to the lost souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.45,0:24:17.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)}A fabricated smile is a false remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:20.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)}With each meeting comes a farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:24.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)}There is no longer any reason to seek warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.58,0:24:28.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)}And yet... he smiled.